OL,3,CThe history of steelmaking in Port
OL,4,CTalbot
OL,6,F1901-05: The original Port Talbot
OL,7,Fsteel mill is built in the Welsh town.
OL,8,FIt is named after Christopher Rice
OL,9,FMansel Talbot.
OL,11,F1901-1910: William Gilbertson began
OL,12,Fconstructing the Port Talbot
OL,13,Fsteelworks, having chosen the location
OL,14,Fbecause of its proximity both to the
OL,15,Fdocks and railway. However, it failed
OL,16,Fwithin a year of production starting.
