OL,3,CThe history of steelmaking in Port
OL,4,CTalbot
OL,6,F1938: Construction of Blast Furnace 3
OL,7,Fand the re-build of Blast Furnaces 1 &
OL,8,F2 to increase capacity.
OL,10,F1951: A new steel plant, called the
OL,11,FAbbey Works, is opened. It is the
OL,12,Flocation where the current plant
OL,13,Fstands. Two years later it becomes
OL,14,Ffully operational.
OL,16,F1941: Blast Furnace 3 was put into
OL,17,Foperation at the Margam works.
OL,19,F1947: The Steel Company of Wales is
OL,20,Fformed.
