OL,3,CThe history of steelmaking in Port
OL,4,CTalbot
OL,6,F1951: A state-of-the-art hot strip
OL,7,Fmill was put into operation there
OL,8,Ffollowed by modern open-hearth plant
OL,9,Fwith eight furnaces.
OL,11,F1953: Margam Iron and Steel works
OL,12,Fcloses.
OL,14,F1956-1959: Blast Furnace number 4 and
OL,15,Fnumber 5 were constructed.
OL,17,F1961: Original Port Talbot steel mill
OL,18,Fcloses.
